<tool id="CONVERTER_vcf_to_bcf" name="VCF to BCF" version="1.0.0">
    <description />
    <requirements>
        <requirement type="package" version="1.2">bcftools</requirement>
    </requirements>
    <stdio>
        <exit_code description="Error" level="fatal" range="1:" />
    </stdio>
    <command>bcftools view "${input}" -o "${output}" -O b</command>
    <inputs>
        <param format="vcf" label="VCF file" name="input" type="data" />
    </inputs>
    <outputs>
        <data format="bcf" name="output" />
    </outputs>
    <tests>
        <test>
            <param ftype="vcf" name="input" value="test_converter.vcf" />
            <output file="test_converter.bcf" ftype="bcf" lines_diff="4" name="output" />
        </test>
    </tests>
    <help>

**BCFTools Converters**

Conversions between VCF, BCF, and VCF-BGZip.

-----

**Input format**

BCF files, compressed or uncompressed VCF files.

------

**Outputs**

BCF files, compressed or uncompressed VCF files.


        </help>
    <citations>
        <citation type="doi">10.1093/bioinformatics/btp352</citation>
    </citations>
</tool>
